				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Activities & Extracurriculars </h2>
				<div class="content">
					<div class="content">
						<p>Ambassador</p>
						<p>Southeast Hypnosis  | November 2021 - April 2024</p>
						<ul>Analyzed reports in Microsoft Excel and Microsoft Word to conduct demographic and data analysis to identify optimal 
							consumer markets and improve email marketing campaigns with 17,000 subscribers (about the seating capacity of Madison Square Garden).</ul>
						<ul>Collaborate in coordinating events for at least 1,000 attendees with representatives from E1 Motorsports, 
							MD Anderson Cancer Center, United States Army, United States Navy, and United States Marine Corps.</ul>
						<ul>Developed effective advertisements and photographs using Adobe Photoshop and Adobe Lightroom to increase ticket sales.  </ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="content">
					<div class="content">
						<p>Member</p>
						<p>Future Information Technology Professionals  | August 2022 - Present</p>
						<ul>Corresponded with high-level industry professionals from Exxon Mobil, Google, Amazon, and Capgemini. </ul>
						<ul>Communicated in informational business meetings to improve knowledge and communication skills.  </ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills & Interests</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Computer Skills</p>
					<ul>Web Development</ul>
					<ul>Cloud Computing</ul>
					<ul>Oracle SQL Developer</ul>
					<ul>MongoDB</ul>
					<ul>MySQL</ul>
